text: T. Rex Autopsy is a 2015 documentary when a team of four paleontologists dissect a silicon Tyrannosaurus. The four palentologists were Tori Herridge, Stephen Brusatte, Matthew T. Mossbrucker and Luke Gamble, who is the lead anatomist. The T. rex was based off the most complete fossil, "Sue". ==Related pages== * Tyrannosaurus anatomy Category:2015 documentary movies Category:American documentary movies Category:Movies about dinosaurs
title: T. Rex Autopsy
